@baseUrl = http://localhost:8080

### Healthcheck
GET {{baseUrl}}/health

### Emitir lote manual de Invoices
POST {{baseUrl}}/admin/invoices/issue-now

### Listar Invoices locais
GET {{baseUrl}}/admin/invoices

### Listar batches locais
GET {{baseUrl}}/admin/invoice-batches

### Listar eventos de webhook locais
GET {{baseUrl}}/admin/webhook-events

### Listar Transfers locais
GET {{baseUrl}}/admin/transfers

### Webhook ilustrativo sem assinatura válida
# Este exemplo não substitui um webhook real da Stark Bank.
# O endpoint real exige Digital-Signature válido, gerado pela Stark Bank.
# Com esta assinatura placeholder, a resposta esperada é 400.
POST {{baseUrl}}/webhooks/starkbank
Content-Type: application/json
Digital-Signature: placeholder-invalid-signature

{
  "event": {
    "id": "event-placeholder",
    "subscription": "invoice",
    "log": {
      "id": "log-placeholder",
      "type": "paid",
      "invoice": {
        "id": "invoice-placeholder",
        "status": "paid",
        "amount": 1000,
        "fee": 50
      }
    }
  }
}
